  <brief_title>Combined Effect of Dexamethasone and Paracetamol for Postoperative Sore Throat</brief_title>
  <official_title>Combined Effect of Preoperative Dexamethasone and Intraoperative Paracetamol on Postoperative Sore Throat for Patients Undergoing Urologic Surgery</official_title>
